Funeral Flowers, Condolence Flowers and Gifts
Send Flowers and Gifts for a Funeral Service
The passing of a loved one can be one of the most difficult times that your family and friends may ever face. Show your sympathy by sending a funeral flower arrangementor gift basket sent to the service, the office, or home of your loved ones, friends or coworkers. Many of our funeral flower arrangements include lilies, orchids, roses, carnations and more. Flowers are an excellent way to express your sympathy while giving the loved ones of the departed a beautiful reminder of the love and support that surrounds them. Whether you decide to send a beautiful standing spray or wreath to the service or a simple and elegant sympathy bouquet to the home, 1-800-Flowers has options for every need and budget.

    Sympathy Gift Baskets and Gourmet Food
Sending condolence flowers to someone or a group who is grieving can be a strong reminder of the recipient's support network and all of the people who care about them. Gift baskets and gourmet food baskets can be an excellent alternative to the traditional gift of flowers and in some religious funeral traditions, may even be a more appropriate sympathy gift than flowers. Sympathy gift baskets offer multiple options and variety to brighten any home when in mourning. Choose 1-800-Flowers for your sympathy gift and funeral flower needs to make sure you can express your sympathy and offer comfort for those that are grieving.
    
Sympathy & Remembrance Resources

    Get helpful information & resources from our sympathy experts on our sympathy content hub. From funeral customs by religion to what you should send to a funeral or wake, get our recommendations to make a difficult time a little easier.
    
