Flower Arrangements
Whether you are celebrating Mother's Day, Christmas, Birthdays, Weddings, baby shower or any other happy event, you can rest easy knowing that all you have to do is pick up the phone or click to our website and you can reach our customer center where you can benefit from the advice and help of the world's largest florist. Read moreHide more

1-800-FLOWERS.COM® called that for the union of technology and flower deliver that we pioneered, has been delivering flowers to our customers since 1976. We deal in flowers for all occasion but our specialization is making our customers happy. We guarantee satisfaction and have built a network with local florists and flower growers.  Our position in the florist industry ensures that the flowers you send are delivered on time and will be as fresh, beautiful and fragrant as possible. Our customer service team is dedicated to your satisfaction and is standing by to help you with any order, whether you need a dozen roses to celebrate your love or if you need a special gift of plants, gift baskets, gourmet foods or stuffed animals.

                Any florist has flowers but nobody has the number and quality of choices we offer. In addition to the widest variety of fresh colorful flowers including roses, tulips, carnations, orchids, tulips and more, you can also choose live plants and an enormous selection of delicious baskets of fresh fruit, chocolate and candy.

                Shop at 1-800-FLOWERS.com® for any occasion that calls for flowers: anniversaries, just because, new baby, love and romance, I'm sorry, get well, and Sympathy. We also have the perfect flowers and floral arrangements and centerpieces for Valentines Day, Mother's Day, Father's Day, Christmas, New Year's, Thanksgiving and Halloween. Whatever your occasion, whatever you favorite color, we have all your favorite flowers and gift choices.

                When you send a delivery bouquet or gift from 1-800-FLOWERS.com® you can expect the best quality flowers and the fastest delivery. Same day flower delivery is available anytime of the year: spring, summer, winter or fall. All you have to do is place your order by 2:00 of the gift receiver's time.

                Why does 1-800-FLOWERS.com® have such a great reputation? Because as an online provider we can use technology to provide better, faster service. Most importantly: as big as we have grown, we never forget that our customers must always come first.. Providing excellent customer service is our highest priority and we prove it every day. Our team is standing by to take your information and help you with any order. Whether you're sending a dozen roses to celebrate your love or gift baskets for the largest corporate event-worker—our team is ready to help. Just call 1-800-356-9377 or place your order online. We will help you find and deliver the perfect flowers, plants, or gift to celebrate holidays and special occasions.

                A Forbes Magazine Best of the Web pick, and named to Internet Retailer's Best of the Web Top 50 Retail Sites list for seven consecutive years, 1-800-FLOWERS.com® is proud to offer solutions for every gifting need, whether you're looking for flower delivery across town or across the country.

                Need flowers delivered in England? Visit our England Flower Delivery page.


















































