 Same-Day Local Florist Delivery
























































From the very moment you hear of a loss you can send a fresh bouquet, plant, or standing arrangement to any location through 1-800-Flowers.com. Same-day sympathy flowers are designed to let them know that you care and support them during this difficult period in life. Even when you can't be there in person, a well-thought out flower arrangement or plant can serve as a constant reminder of your presence within their hearts. When you need to send sympathy flowers the very same day, 1-800-FLOWERS.COM® can help you send an appropriate and thoughtful gift.
Sending the Perfect Sympathy Flowers
When selecting same-day sympathy flowers you can choose from a variety of bouquets that are appropriate for homes, offices, and funerals. Traditionally, sympathy flowers are designed with a variety of fresh white flowers including white roses, spider mums, carnations, snapdragons and other pale stems. Vibrant red, white, yellow, purple, or pink combinations are also appropriate and help to infuse color and life during an otherwise painful time. Depending on the funeral service you can choose from a wide assortment of quality standing sprays, wreaths, floor baskets, standing baskets, and tableside arrangements. Other options, including elegant floor or basket plants, can become a long-lasting reminder of your support well after the services have ended.
1-800-FLOWERS.COM® is available to support and assistance you during your purchase process. Same-day sympathy flowers can be sent in minutes through a reliable and secure site designed to help you choose the most appropriate flowers to express your condolences. You can rest assure that your flowers will arrive to your destination to let them know you care. If the day arrives that you must choose sympathy flowers for a friend, family member, or colleague let 1-800-Flowers.com guide you and help you send the very best flowers and plants.
    
